       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI10602.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI10602.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Inserçăo Débitos/Créditos Diversos                         *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI10602         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6702 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3605 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV1060.
       COPY COCV1061.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT6702 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6702'.
           05 CON-COVT3605 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3605'.
           05 CON-SEP      PIC X(01) VALUE '/'.
           05 CON-999      PIC X(03) VALUE '999'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME            PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI10602'.
           05 WS-NIDINVOICE          PIC  9(10) VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-DATA-AUX            PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DATA-AUX.
              10 WS-DATA-AUX-ANO     PIC  X(4).
              10 WS-DATA-AUX-SEP1    PIC  X(1).
              10 WS-DATA-AUX-MES     PIC  X(2).
              10 WS-DATA-AUX-SEP2    PIC  X(1).
              10 WS-DATA-AUX-DIA     PIC  X(2).
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI10602         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *    CALL 'ARREBENTA'.
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT      TO COCV1060-MSG.
           MOVE COCV1060-ASE                 TO COCV1061-ASE.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1060-ADE       TO COCV1061-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2900-VER-PROJECTO
                 THRU 2900-VER-PROJECTO-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2100-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-OBTEM-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Ver se existe na tabela COT67_EXPENSES a factura AAAA/999
           MOVE COCV1060-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCV1060-DDATAEMIS2   TO WS-DATA-AUX.
           MOVE WS-DATA-AUX-ANO       TO COCD6702-GREFINV(1:4).
           MOVE CON-SEP               TO COCD6702-GREFINV(5:1).
           MOVE CON-999               TO COCD6702-GREFINV(6:3).

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  GREFINV
                     ,  NIDINVOICE
                     ,  NIDPROJECTO
                     ,  GCLIENTE
                     ,  NTOTALAMOUNT
                     ,  NTAXAMOUNT
                  INTO :COCD6702-GREFINV
                     , :COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                     , :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
                     , :COCD6702-GCLIENTE
                     , :COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD6702-NTAXAMOUNT
                  FROM  COVT6702_EXPENSES
                 WHERE  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
                 AND    GREFINV     = :COCD6702-GREFINV
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6702  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE COCV1060-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO
                 MOVE COCD6702-NIDINVOICE   TO COCV1061-NIDINVOICE
                 MOVE COCV1060-DDATAEMIS2   TO COCV1061-DDATAEMIS2
                 MOVE COCD3605-CMOEDA       TO COCV1061-CMOEDA
              ELSE
                 MOVE COCV1060-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO
                 PERFORM 2122-VER-NIDINVOICE
                    THRU 2122-VER-NIDINVOICE-EXIT
                 MOVE WS-NIDINVOICE         TO COCV1061-NIDINVOICE
                 MOVE COCV1060-DDATAEMIS2   TO COCV1061-DDATAEMIS2
                 MOVE COCD3605-CMOEDA       TO COCV1061-CMOEDA
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2100-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2122-VER-NIDINVOICE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2122-VER-NIDINVOICE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2122-VER-NIDINVOICE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1060-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  IFNULL(MAX(NIDINVOICE), 0) + 1
                  INTO :COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                  FROM  COVT6702_EXPENSES
                 WHERE  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.


           MOVE CON-COVT6702  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE COCD6702-NIDINVOICE      TO WS-NIDINVOICE
           END-IF.

       2122-VER-NIDINVOICE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2900-VER-PROJECTO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2900-VER-PROJECTO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2900-VER-PROJECTO ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1060-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT  CLIENTE
                      ,  CMOEDA
                      ,  ICTACUST
                      ,  BACTIVE
                   INTO :COCD3605-CLIENTE
                      , :COCD3605-CMOEDA
                      , :COCD3605-ICTACUST
                      , :COCD3605-BACTIVE
                 FROM    COVT3605_PROJECTS
                 WHERE   NIDPROJECTO = :COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT3605 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF NOT DB2-OK
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                  TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO-S
                MOVE COCK0001-NIDPROJECTO-N-EXISTS
                  TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                  TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  DB2-OK
             AND COCD3605-BACTIVE NOT = COCK0002-BACTIVE-ACTIVO
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-NIDPROJECTO-INV
                   TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  DB2-OK
             AND COCD3605-ICTACUST NOT = COCK0002-SIM
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-NIDPROJECTO-INV
                   TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV1061-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2900-VER-PROJECTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV1061-GDESCINVOICE'   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV1061-GDESCINVOICE    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV1061-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV1061-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV1061-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
